<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="brain-n">brain <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /breɪn/    美 /breɪn/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>大脑：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The left half of the brain controls the right side of the body. 
左脑支配身体的右半部。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.<strong>头脑；智力；智慧：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The job requires brains.
这工作需要动脑筋。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Teachers spotted that he had a good brain at an early age. 
老师们发现他从小就很聪明。</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.<strong>聪明的人；智囊：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Some of the best brains in our company are here tonight. 
今晚我们公司的一些智囊人物云集于此。</p></div></div>